1973;;Never Mind the Quality Feel the Width;;British;;Ronnie Baxter;;John Bluthal, Joe Lynch, Yootha Joyce;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Never_Mind_the_Quality_Feel_the_Width_(film);;In the course of the film, Manny and Patrick hire a sexy new assistant Rita, seriously fall out after a gambling incident, experience woman trouble, find themselves burgled, and eventually end up on holiday in Rome after posing as priests.[2]